{"tid":1366170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727] 你貼連儂牆有冇申請不反對通知書？去何妖辦事處有冇？","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:10:09.000Z","uid":161430,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6269a534e19bcf723dc26ca620fc27cb84100f79","tid":1366170,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:22:41.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時d乜乜乜突發 邊度要人既事，又需唔需要通知書？唔駛。<br />\n<br />\n入元朗駛乜諗乜野理由？諗咁多即係已經屈服左喺佢既白色恐怖入面，入左佢畫比你既框入面，唔敢走出框外。<br />\n<br />\n而且根本基本法，香港人係有集會自由。<br />\n<br />\n真係驚比人問，直接答入黎行街，星期六放假呀大佬，放心，人夠多就可以。<br />\n<br />\n反黑係理直氣壯呀各位"},{"pid":"556f697df762a6379b8855f425763f0907ae88a9","tid":1366170,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249e6b230bc7311c3b34037d231d9aefda8dcacf","tid":1366170,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"賓賓 印印明目張膽都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fce5e8c543ebda4e805b8b4890444c355a11f31","tid":1366170,"uid":161430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"249e6b230bc7311c3b34037d231d9aefda8dcacf","tid":1366170,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"賓賓 印印明目張膽都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"根本就係<br />\n<br />\n點解平時連登仔話我地宜家去邊度辦事處 去日牛 貼連儂牆又唔諗張通知書，但今次元朗就自己不停諗呢張通知書？<br />\n<br />\n唔駛比人嚇窒喎，你唔係連出街權利都冇掛，仲有跟基本法你有集會自由"},{"pid":"897f695282ac1a394fb9cd8d9432b6b3a5240036","tid":1366170,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0791c9fcc8f603a1375842f760eab5b594c51710","tid":1366170,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523826069fd01cbaf648cedbebc44383ab9e93c9","tid":1366170,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:49:13.000Z","msg":"我問多一句 你地自己諗<br />\n<br />\n除左連儂牆，咁以前佔領你去金鐘旺角條馬路都冇比人話非法集結，點解因為今次佢唔批不反對通知書你就反而要諗唔同理由入元朗，驚自己唔可以接照基本法下去遊行？<br />\n<br />\n你行果條路仲要唔係非法佔返黎"},{"pid":"9f1879ff72ac5688017dd7872141eac421c1b7d7","tid":1366170,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要講清楚<br />\n何妖辦事處係比人追數攪，唔好屈其他人</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ec0cc569f004a668bcd992c3f7fd2c9ce807b4f","tid":1366170,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqOzi.png&h=002dc61c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n更新左加入更多地標, 遊行路線, 有意見隨時回答, 謝"}]}